’Ù@f970d8fde749b4f9b4e03426bd38bd3acf9d15b4f510ebd0c9a465f99dd89b39ÚTitle: title: term query
Path: Flags
Content:
``--prefix, -p {oneof<binary, string>}``
: Prefix sequence for the expected reply.
``--terminator, -t {oneof<binary, string>}``
: Terminator sequence for the expected reply.
``--keep, -k``
: Include prefix and terminator in the output.
